OL,3,CAlleged $4 billion 'Cryptoqueen'
OL,4,Cscammer hid assets in Guernsey
OL,6,FOne of the world's most prolific
OL,7,Falleged scammers, who is believed to
OL,8,Fhave helped defraud victims out of
OL,9,Fmore than $4 billion, hid millions of
OL,10,Fpounds of assets in Guernsey shell
OL,11,Fcompanies.
OL,13,FDr Ruja Ignatova, who rose to fame as
OL,14,Fthe 'Cryptoqueen' after founding the
OL,15,Fdigital currency OneCoin, is on the
OL,16,FFBI's most wanted list - with a reward
OL,17,Fof up to $5 million offered for
OL,18,Finformation leading to her arrest and
OL,19,Fconviction.
