OL,3,CAlleged $4 billion 'Cryptoqueen'
OL,4,Cscammer hid assets in Guernsey
OL,6,FNow it has emerged that the 45-year-
OL,7,Fold, who is a Bulgaria-born German
OL,8,Fcitizen, owed two London properties,
OL,9,Fincluding a penthouse, through shell
OL,10,Fcompanies in Guernsey - which were
OL,11,Fsold for a combined #11.4 million.
OL,13,FCarsten Nowak, a senior German Public
OL,14,FProsecutor who handles high-profile
OL,15,Feconomic corruption cases, told ITV
OL,16,FChannel that the funds used to buy
OL,17,Fthese homes were from deposits made by
OL,18,Fsome of the Cryptoqueen's alleged
OL,19,Fvictims.
