OL,3,CAlleged $4 billion 'Cryptoqueen'
OL,4,Cscammer hid assets in Guernsey
OL,6,FMr Nowak's office has therefore
OL,7,Fapplied to the Guernsey authorities to
OL,8,Fconfiscate the proceeds of these sales.
OL,10,FHis latest information suggests that,
OL,11,Fafter costs and taxes, approximately
OL,12,F#8.8 million remains in a business
OL,13,Fbank account based on the island.
OL,15,FHis Majesty's Comptroller, Crown
OL,16,FAdvocate Hilary Pullum, applied to
OL,17,FGuernsey's Royal Court on 24 October
OL,18,Fto enforce an overseas forfeiture
OL,19,Forder.
