OL,3,CAlleged $4 billion 'Cryptoqueen'
OL,4,Cscammer hid assets in Guernsey
OL,6,FIt essentially means that unless Dr
OL,7,FRuja Ignatova or anyone else objects
OL,8,Fby 16 December to her assets being
OL,9,Fconfiscated, the funds are likely to
OL,10,Fbe handed over to the German
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FThe application is expected to be
OL,14,Fheard at the Royal Court on Tuesday 13
OL,15,FJanuary at 10am.
OL,17,FIf released, Mr Nowak says the money
OL,18,Fwould be used to repay some of the
OL,19,Falleged victims in Germany.
